b'How to value a SPAC before the merger

The "pro forma" market cap is based on a share price of $10. If the SP is higher, the post-merger valuation will be higher, too.

Example $OAC/ HIMS:
At $15.68 per share, the implied market cap is actually $2.978B, not $1.927B. https://t.co/7h9hme9TYe'
